snippet.title: Concord - Beta Trailer I PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playconcord.com

Be among the first to play Concord* during our Open Beta Weekends: 
Early Access: July 12 – 14 
Open Beta: July 18 - 21 

Play All 16 Characters. 3 PVP Modes. 4 Maps. Earn Beta Rewards. Concord launches August 23, 2024. To stay up to date, follow @PlayConcord on social media. 

*Account for PlayStation™Network and internet connection required.

#ps5 #ps5games #pcgames #concord
